Package: sd-keepaneye
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends},
    adduser,
    python3-dbus,
    python3-systemd,
Description: Keeping an eye on systemd
 sd-keepaneye is designed to provide mail notifications upon systemd jobs
 failure (like cron has been mailing stderr output. It consists in a daemon
 that listen to events on systemd D-Bus interface.
